author: jdonnerstag
msg: by means of Component.setRenderComponentTag(boolean) it is now easily possible to disable writing a component's tag. This is e.g. necessary with <span> tags and Panels where in cases where you want to be strictly HTML compliant the <span> tag must be removed. The (tag's) body is not affected by this setting
